sentences: The review of the Protocol was taken up in consultations throughout the day, and in the evening as part of a ministerial meeting.

Following Chair Tudela Abad introduction of draft text on Thursday morning, progress was made on the text, but differences remained on issues including a confidence clause specifying that the review will not lead to non-Annex I commitments, and the dates for the next review, with proposals ranging from 2 to 5 years.
The text reportedly remained bracketed as of midnight.
